        {
          "block_label": "figure_title",
          "block_content": "Figure30.44 Productionofa hologram.Single-wavelengthcoherent lightfrom a laser produces a well-definedinterference patternon a pieceoffilm.Thelaserbeamissplitbpartiallsilveredmrrorwithpartofthelihtiluminatintheobjctandtheremaindershiningdirctlonthefilm.",
